Subscribe to this Add-On to make your map more colorful when zoomed in.

Activate both this Add-On and Theatrum Orbis Terrarum in your launcher.

This Add-On is compatible with all other Add-Ons.

Special Thanks to
[b]Negi[/b] for the magic code that makes transparency dynamic and his effort on porting it to 1.19

